description:
Epic coot slap fight!  2 coots going at it nonstop for more than 10 minutes.  2 had some huge problem with each other and would rear up and kick at each other and peck/bite.  Occasionally another 1-3 random passerby coots would come charging in and hit indiscriminately at either of the pair for a while before departing.  Strange!  

Videos: 
1.) https://youtu.be/Tbt5NdC_w78 (many coots pile on)
